&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS/BA in a scientific discipline required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of experience in medical research, laboratory, histology, IVD, nursing, or the biopharmaceutical industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 2 years of laboratory experience, including specimen processing and molecular assay testing&lt;/li&gt;
