&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on the design, implementation, administration, and governance of employee compensation, health and welfare, and retirement benefit plans, including equity incentive plans, ESPPs, and deferred compensation arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide legal support on executive and director compensation programs, including severance, change‑in‑control, and employment arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on 401(k) and welfare plan governance, fiduciary oversight, and related ERISA matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with ERISA, the Internal Revenue Code, ACA, HIPAA, COBRA, and other applicable laws and regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and interpret legislative and regulatory developments affecting compensation and benefits programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support M&amp;amp;A activity in close collaboration with Human Resources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Public Company / Governance / Securities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
