&lt;li&gt;Provide legal advice on compensation‑related disclosure and corporate governance matters, including the Company’s Annual Proxy Statement and annual shareholder meeting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Section 16 compliance, including preparation and filing of Forms 3, 4, and 5.&lt;/li&gt;
