&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;As a Customer Care Specialist, you will be the cornerstone of our customer care team. Your primary mission is to ensure that healthcare providers and patients receive unparalleled service and support. You will handle customer inquiries with empathy, professionalism, and efficiency. By actively collaborating with internal teams such as Sales, Laboratory, and Billing, you will resolve issues promptly and enhance the overall customer experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;ESSENTIAL DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Order Management: Efficiently manage and monitor orders and cases from submission to completion, ensuring timely resolutions and clear communication with customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Physician Outreach: Perform outbound communication with physician offices through phone fax, email, and other channels to efficiently resolve order issues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
