&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a talented and experienced data scientist III (contractor) to join our Data Analysis Team (DAT), as part of the R&amp;amp;D group for Veracyte Inc. This position offers a unique opportunity to work with experienced professionals to carry out AI/ML modelling and analysis of the world’s largest database of cancer patients, encompassing multi-platform digital pathology, genomic and clinical outcome data.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
