&lt;p&gt;The Executive Director, Discovery, is a key R&amp;amp;D leadership role and will participate in shaping scientific strategy, portfolio planning, and discovery operations that fuel product innovation. This individual will also provide scientific leadership during early-stage business development opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
