&lt;p&gt;The Manager, IT &amp;amp; Cybersecurity GRC (Governance, Risk, and Compliance) leads the design, execution, and continuous improvement of enterprise technology controls and risk management programs. This role is accountable for managing IT SOX compliance, advancing enterprise risk management (ERM) initiatives, and strengthening cybersecurity governance across a highly regulated environment. You will partner cross‑functionally to translate risk into actionable insights, elevate control maturity, and support business growth while ensuring regulatory alignment.&lt;/p&gt;
