&lt;li&gt;Build, coach, and retain a high-performing Product and UX team; define roles, career paths, hiring plans, and development expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and own the multi-quarter product strategy, business case, and roadmap for Veracyte’s core technology platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align product planning to enterprise needs, ensuring shared technology capabilities support multiple clinical product launches and business growth.&lt;/li&gt;
